de.ityx.mediatrix.api.interfaces

Interface IViewFilter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IInfo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ViewFilter

    public interface IViewFilter
extends IInfo
    Describes the objects that are used to filter the mail inbox objects. Only the objects(SingleMode) are visible that are matched by the view filters.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int VF_PROJECT
      It' the project's filter.
      static int VF_SUBPROJECT
      It' the subproject's filter.
      static int VF_SUBPROJECT_DEFAULT
      The subproject isn't set.
